<h1>红</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">hóng</span><span class=alesi>(hong2)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">gōng</span><span class=alesi>(gong1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 红 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 红</h2><div class=abo>
